summary: An ordinance extending the Manufacturing District at 3rd Avenue West and West Nickerson Street to include Blocks 54, 69, 70 and that portion of Block 55, lying north of West Nickerson Street all in Denny and Hoyt's Addition, also the triangular parcel of land bounded by West Bertona Street, Lake Washington Canal and Queen Anne Avenue and amending Ordinance No. 45382 as amended.
